; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0;"><strong>Negotiation at Sc=
ale.</strong> Outfit orders all of the materials and tools for its customer=
s and coordinates deliveries, meaning that it can get discounts with vendor=
s beyond what a general Pro gets.</p></li><li style=3D"margin: 3.75px 0 3.7=
