t: 1.16em; margin: 1em 0 0.625em 0;"><strong>Ian: Product-Founder Fit</stro=
ng></h3><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; mar=
gin: 0 0 1em 0;">Like most of the deals we do in the Not Boring Syndicate, =
